'''硝酸铪'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为Hf(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>4</sub>，可用于含铪材料的制备。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Electrochemical and Solid-State Letters|volume=5|issue=5|language=en|date=2002|pages=C57|doi=10.1149/1.1462875|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1149/1.1462875|title=Atomic Layer Deposition of Hafnium Oxide Using Anhydrous Hafnium Nitrate|accessdate=2020-04-23|author=J. F. Conley, Y. Ono, W. Zhuang, D. J. Tweet, W. Gao, S. K. Mohammed, R. Solanki|archive-date=2021-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211029210622/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1149/1.1462875|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==制备及性质==
硝酸铪由[[四氯化铪|四氯化铪]]和[[五氧化二氮|五氧化二氮]]反应得到。<ref name=weiwei />硝酸铪受热经[[硝酸氧铪|HfO(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>]]最终得到[[二氧化铪|HfO<sub>2</sub>]]。<ref>Tuseev, N. I.; Izmailovich, A. S.; Komissarova, L. N. Anhydrous tetranitrates of titanium, zirconium, hafnium, and tin. ''Vestnik Moskovskogo Universiteta, Seriya 2:  Khimiya'', 1979. 20 (5): 453-455. ISSN: 0579-9384.</ref>
